OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781606874
OL,3,CHerd of cows helping restore rare
OL,4,Cwetland habitat
OL,6,FA herd of cows has been brought in to
OL,7,Fhelp restore a rare wetland habitat in
OL,8,FOxfordshire.
OL,10,FFive native Dexter cattle have been
OL,11,Fintroduced to Hinksey Heights, west of
OL,12,FOxford, which is one of a small number
OL,13,Fof alkaline fens.
OL,15,FWith the help of volunteers,
OL,16,FFreshwater Habitats Trust has been
OL,17,Frestoring the habitat since 2018, but
OL,18,Fthe cows are now being used to manage
OL,19,Fvegetation and give rare wetland
OL,20,Fwildlife a chance to thrive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
