PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781606874
OL,3,CHerd of cows helping restore rare
OL,4,Cwetland habitat
OL,6,FOxfordshire has an internationally
OL,7,Fimportant concentration of alkaline
OL,8,Ffens, but many have become degraded or
OL,9,Flost altogether.
OL,11,FAccording to the Freshwater Habitats
OL,12,FTrust, 70 hectares of these wetlands
OL,13,Fhave now been lost across the county -
OL,14,Fan area the size of 100 football
OL,15,Fpitches.
OL,17,FThe Trust spring-fed wetlands are
OL,18,Fvital for biodiversity, supporting
OL,19,Fendangered plants and animals not
OL,20,Ffound in other habitats.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781606874
OL,3,CHerd of cows helping restore rare
OL,4,Cwetland habitat
OL,6,FAt Hinksey Heights, Freshwater
OL,7,FHabitats Trust works with the
OL,8,Flandowner, local ecologists and
OL,9,Fvolunteers to cut dense reeds and
OL,10,Fother competitive plants.
OL,12,FVolunteers meet on the second Sunday
OL,13,Fof every month to clear vegetation by
OL,14,Fscything and raking.
OL,16,FAs well as eating vegetation, the cows
OL,17,Fwill also spread seeds across the site
OL,18,Fon their hooves, and in their fur and
OL,19,Fdung.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781606874
OL,3,CHerd of cows helping restore rare
OL,4,Cwetland habitat
OL,6,FThe cattle will wear GPS-enabled
OL,7,Fcollars, allowing the team to manage
OL,8,Fand monitor where they graze.
OL,10,FActing as 'digital shepherds', the
OL,11,Fcollars emit an audible warning if
OL,12,Fcows approach restricted areas.
OL,14,FDiscussing the decline in fenland
OL,15,Fhabitat, David Morris of the
OL,16,FFreshwater Habitats Trust, said: "It's
OL,17,Fall to do with a decline of
OL,18,Ftraditional management of wetlands,
OL,19,Fsuch as grazing with cows.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781606874
OL,3,CHerd of cows helping restore rare
OL,4,Cwetland habitat
OL,6,F"And without that management tool,
OL,7,Ftall plants take over and swamp out
OL,8,Fall the small special things, such as
OL,9,Fthe Marsh Lousewort that we have
OL,10,Fgrowing around us here."
OL,12,F"And without our work, things like
OL,13,Fthat would simply disappear."
OL,15,FVolunteer John Magrath added: "They're
OL,16,Fgoing to be trampling down the reeds,
OL,17,Fwhich we'd have to cut otherwise, and
OL,18,Fthey're going to be spreading seeds
OL,19,Faround.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781606874
OL,3,CHerd of cows helping restore rare
OL,4,Cwetland habitat
OL,6,F"And in the hoof prints that they
OL,7,Fmake, there's going to be all sorts of
OL,8,Fmicro habitats for lots of plants,
OL,9,Fthey're great."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
